<bibRefCitation author="Li" box="[666,772,295,320]" pageId="15" pageNumber="366" refString="Li, Z. Z. (1993) A new species of Scaphoideus (Homoptera: Euscelidae) from Mt. Emei, Sichuan, China. Entomotaxonomia, 15 (1), 45 - 47. [in Chinese with English summary]" type="journal article" year="1993">Li (1993)</bibRefCitation>
